{"tid":2204972,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「求和」說爭議 央視主持人再辯：是尋「求」「和」平","createTime":"2020-09-16T12:30:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T13:22:56.000Z","uid":290118,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f04aac17e4d10603619e0866903d32c1658a8eaa","tid":2204972,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T12:30:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E6%B1%82%E5%92%8C%E8%AA%AA%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0-%E5%A4%AE%E8%A6%96%E4%B8%BB%E6%8C%81%E4%BA%BA%E5%86%8D%E8%BE%AF%E6%98%AF%E5%B0%8B%E6%B1%82%E5%92%8C%E5%B9%B3-021307401.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%2592%258C%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E7%2588%25AD%25E8%25AD%25B0-%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E8%25A6%2596%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%258C%2581%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%25B0%258B%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%2592%258C%25E5%25B9%25B3-021307401.html&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvctxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=edc86b88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E6%B1%82%E5%92%8C%E8%AA%AA%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0-%E5%A4%AE%E8%A6%96%E4%B8%BB%E6%8C%81%E4%BA%BA%E5%86%8D%E8%BE%AF%E6%98%AF%E5%B0%8B%E6%B1%82%E5%92%8C%E5%B9%B3-021307401.html</a><br />\n王金平參加海峽論壇「求和說」引發爭議，陸方對此頻緩頰，央視主持人李紅昨天再稱「求和」是「尋求和平」，自己本意是促進兩岸溝通與和平。<br />\n引發事端的李紅12日晚間透過中評社表示，自己在節目中的短影片表述「純屬個人，不代表官方」，本意是促進兩岸溝通與和平。她說：「『求』就是『尋求』，『和』就是『和平』，如果完整地看了我的短視頻，您可以清晰地了解我的本意。」<br />\n李紅強調自己主持兩岸節目多年，始終期盼透過交流合作，促進兩岸和平發展，維護台海和平穩定。"},{"pid":"4d12690fd5f76e8c87ee271771476e474b36b29b","tid":2204972,"uid":290118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T12:31:25.000Z","msg":"國台辦都要向張建宗學習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【武漢肺炎】昨稱「疫情受控」捱轟 張建宗今發稿：整體情況正在受嚴密監控<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%98%A8%E7%A8%B1-%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E5%8F%97%E6%8E%A7-%E6%8D%B1%E8%BD%9F-%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97%E4%BB%8A%E7%99%B